<br>
i dont like either way ... but i lived with it.  the guild is by no means &quot;uber&quot;  with only 15 or so 50+ and all but 3 of those are 51s.   myself and Morkai (57 wiz) are the only ones in the guild with real &quot;uber raid&quot; exp. and are trying to gear them up for the cool stuff out there to explore. (raids are more fun without fights over loot)<br>
