<br>
I think the most important thing is that people are there for each other and to help the guild. If they get loot out of it, great.<br>
<br>
My advice go with a point system that is not totally open member bid (for example the druid cant win the cobalt bp that just dropped) or if you have the right guild for it, go with an awards/officer directed system.<br>
<br>
